				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/6/from-the-kitchen">From The Kitchen</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/sy-safransky">Sy Safransky</a> &amp;&nbsp;<a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/mike-mathers">Mike Mathers</a></li><li><a href="/issues/6">October 1974</a></li></ul>

		

